Sheryl Munks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sheryl_Munks 0 Sheryl Munks (born 1965) is an Australian actress. A former dancer of classical ballet, jazz ballet and tap, as well as a dance instructor. She is best known to audiences for her role as inmate Michelle "Brumby" Tucker in the television series Prisoner. Sheryl_Munks ( born 1965 ) is an_Australian_actress .
